<div class="fullscreen container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-8">
      <div class="row d-flex align-items-center" id="headline">
        <div class="container">
          <div>
            <h1>Create. Collaborate. Control.</h1>
            <p>Feedbacker offers a new way for artists to create freely, get feedback on their progress and develop the best art they can. </p>
            <div class="button-wrapper">
              <a href="#" class="button-tertiary-shadow">Sign up for free now</a>
              <a href="#" class="button-shadow">Sign up for free now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row"> 
        <div class="col border-right-landing small-headlines d-flex align-items-end">
          <div>
            <h6>Be in control.</h6>
            <p>You are in charge of the privacy features regarding your work. Decide wheter you want to keep your drafts private or public.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col border-right-landing d-flex align-items-end">
          <div>
            <h6>Find a community.</h6>
            <p>Feedbacker is a collection of like-minded creatives that share the same values and want to progress with their work.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col border-right-landing d-flex align-items-end">
          <div>
            <h6>Progress with your work.</h6>
            <p>Feedback is the best way to learn and progress with your art. You can learn a lot and ultimately create the best version yourself.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" id="landing-image">
          <!-- <%= image_tag "landing.jpg", style:'max-height: 90%' %> -->
          <%= cl_image_tag "landing_hnmglg", style:'max-height: 90%' %>  
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col border-right-landing landing-link text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <%= link_to  "Log In", root_path%>
        </div>
        <div class="col border-right-landing landing-link d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <%= link_to  "Sign Up Free", root_path%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>